:Bromocriptine :hasReference :R104 .
:Bromocriptine :hasReference :R016 .
:Bromocriptine :hasReference :R014 .
:Bromocriptine :hasSubstanceDescription "The Parlodel brand of bromocriptine is used to treat certain conditions caused by a hormone imbalance in which there is too much prolactin in the blood (hyperprolactinemia). High prolactin levels may cause sexual problems, hot flashes, menstrual problems or infertility in women, muscle loss in men, breast enlargement in men and women, and lack of sexual development in adolescents. Parlodel is also used to treat these disorders when they are caused by a noncancerous tumor of the pituitary gland that can overproduce prolactin." .

:Caffeine :hasSubstanceDescription "Caffeine is a central nervous system stimulant. It works by stimulating the brain. Caffeine is found naturally in foods and beverages such as coffee, tea, colas, energy and chocolate. Botanical sources of caffeine include kola nuts, guarana, and yerba mate. Caffeine is also available in prescription and non-prescription medications." .
:Caffeine :hasReference :R123 .
:Caffeine :hasReference :R025 .
:Caffeine :hasReference :R026 .

