:Cyclosporine :hasReference :R026 .
:Cyclosporine :hasReference :R010 .
:Cyclosporine :hasReference :R005 .
:Cyclosporine :hasSubstanceDescription "Cyclosporine weakens your body's immune system, to help keep it from \"rejecting\" a transplanted organ such as a kidney. Organ rejection happens when the immune system treats the new organ as an invader and attacks it." .

