:ITN003 :hasInteractionDescription "Concomitant therapy of tetracycline with anticoagulants may result to prolongation of prothrombin time. Reduction of dose may be necessary." .
:ITN003 :hasReference :R003 .
:ITN003 :interactsWith :Anticoagulants .

:ITN004 :hasInteractionDescription "Prolongation of prothrombin time has been reported rarely in patients receiving amoxicillin. Appropriate monitoring should be undertaken when anticoagulants are prescribed concomitantly." .
:ITN004 :hasReference :R013 .
:ITN004 :interactsWith :Anticoagulants .

:ITN005 :hasInteractionDescription "Increased prothrombin time, with or without clinical bleeding, has been reported." .
