:ITN016 :interactsWith :Antacids .
:ITN016 :hasInteractionDescription "Giving azithromycin with antacids containing aluminum or magnesium salts can reduce the rate, but not the extent, of its absorption; azithromycin should be given at least 1 hour before or 2 hours after the antacid." .
