:Procainamide :hasReference :R115 .
:Procainamide :hasReference :R020 .
:Procainamide :hasSubstanceDescription "Procainamide is used to help keep the heart beating normally in people with certain heart rhythm disorders of the ventricles (the lower chambers of the heart that allow blood to flow out of the heart)." .

:ProcaineLocalAnesthesia :hasSubstanceDescription "Penicillin G procaine, a natural penicillin, is a β-lactam antibiotic. The drug is the procaine monohydrate salt of penicillin G and is a long-acting formulation of penicillin G." .
:ProcaineLocalAnesthesia :hasReference :R020 .
:ProcaineLocalAnesthesia :hasReference :R114 .

:ProgesteroneContraceptives :hasSubstanceDescription "Progestin-only contraceptives (POPs) contain just one hormone, progestin. Most work by thickening cervical mucus, preventing sperm from entering the uterus." .
:ProgesteroneContraceptives :hasReference :R022 .
:ProgesteroneContraceptives :hasReference :R038 .
:ProgesteroneContraceptives :hasReference :R021 .

:Pyrazinamide :hasReference :R014 .
:Pyrazinamide :hasReference :R094 .
:Pyrazinamide :hasSubstanceDescription "Pyrazinamide is an antibiotic that fights bacteria. Pyrazinamide is used to treat tuberculosis (TB) in adults and children." .

:Quinidine :hasReference :R014 .
:Quinidine :hasReference :R095 .
:Quinidine :hasSubstanceDescription "Quinidine is used to help keep the heart beating normally in people with certain heart rhythm disorders, usually after other treatments have failed. Quinidine has not been proven to lower the risks of stroke or death." .

