:SE059 :hasSideEffectDescription "Erythroderma is one alternative name of Exfoliative dermatitis. It is widespread readness of the skin. It also accompanied by scaling, peeling, and flaking of the skin, and may include utching and hair loss." .
:SE059 :hasPattern :Uncommon .

