:Tetracyclines :hasSubstanceDescription "Tetracyclines are a class of antibiotics that may be used to treat infections caused by susceptible microorganisms such as gram positive and gram negative bacteria, chlamydiae, mycoplasma, protozoans, or rickettsiae." .
:Tetracyclines :hasReference :R088 .
:Tetracyclines :hasReference :R013 .

